summary: When Apple keeps reminding you to update your macOS..and you don’t want to cuz you like your same old ,same old OS Sierra and...
body:
When Apple keeps reminding you to update your macOS..and you don’t want to cuz you like your same old ,same old OS Sierra and does not give a damn about the dark mode feature of Mojave….

This is probably 1/10000000000 of how the Doctor feels when he is regenerating. New face, new features, same doctor. New OS, new interface, same trusty old Mac. Anyways idk what my point is but every time I click that “Remind me later” button i know I am just prolonging the inevitable…

summary: #HorrorMovieMarathon Film #  88 Fright Night  (2011) 106 minutes   Color   Rated  R Directed by:  Craig Gillespie Starring:...
caption:
#HorrorMovieMarathon


Film #  88
Fright Night  (2011) 106 minutes   Color   Rated  R
Directed by:  Craig Gillespie
Starring:  Anton Yelchin, Colin Farrell, David Tennant


Meet the sexy new neighbor, Jerry Dandrige. He’s dangerously charming - and utterly lethal. That’s because he just happens to be a vampire, and out for blood… buckets of it. After high school senior Charley Brewster makes the connection between Jerry’s suspicious activity and a steadily rising body count, he vows to end the reign of terror next door. But he can’t do it alone. His only hope is Las Vegas magician/vampire slayer Peter Vincent. Together, this unlikely duo  set out to end Jerry’s evil rampage. But Jerry is a ruthless, relentless killer, and he’s not going down without a fight. Get set to sink your teeth into this thrilling re-vamp of the terrifying horror classic. 


IMDb:  After a new neighbor moved into the house next door, Charley discovers that he is an ancient vampire and goes in search for the help of Peter Vincent, a famous “vampire killer” to save his neighborhood from the creature.
